TestUnknownChannelThrowsTypedError
/ Failure matrix: actor.channel["nope"] selecting an absent channel from PLang code raises
/ a typed error — uniform with goal/type index-miss, no silent noop, no implicit create.
/ Asserts the typed Error.Key, not just "any error" — proves the registry index-miss path,
/ not a null-channel coincidence.
- write 'ping' to absent-channel-xyz, on error set %errorKey% = %!error.Key%
- assert %errorKey% equals 'ChannelNotFound'
